data.description: This spacious updated home with three bedrooms is located on a manicured 1+/- acre lot.  The living room is flanked by a wood-burning fireplace and is open to the kitchen and dining areas. Recent updates include windows, fresh paint, ductwork, registers, electric garage doors, flooring, electrical fixtures, plumbing fixtures, 8' cedar fence, and pull-down stairs in the garage. The guest bath has fresh tile, mirror & vanity. The property is fully fenced. Huge workshop with electricity and large rolling shop doors. Large covered back patio to sit and relax and enjoy the country life!
